# The live site needs only the runtime text layer, which stays tracked:
#   - the data-edit="…" attributes in the page HTML
#   - content.js   (fetches and applies content.json)
#   - content.json (the editor's output — the text the site shows)
#
# Everything below is local-only build/agent tooling and must not be published.
